_sText:
henlo it new map from pretzL & Roz

surf_kairo began as a project by Roz, which he eventually became unhappy with and left to collect dust. Because I've always believed in him as a mapper, I wanted to attempt to showcase how good he really is at making surf. This is my attempt to do so. The surf of the main map as well as 2 bonuses are by him, the name and the theme came from him. I just put things together, got some bonuses from some other people and detailed it all.

This one's for not only a great mapper, but also a good friend.

Map is a T5 linear with 6 bonuses total. Credits for everything can be found on your right.
B4 is not filtered on purpose. May the most retarded route win, or if server owners want to filter it in some way, be my guest.
